      "span_text": "Thus, when we injected with dexamethasone WT mice we observed a significant increase in 5-LO activation and Ab formation, which were completely abolished in mice that were genetically deficient for the 5-LO. Since previous work indicated that 5-LO alters Ab formation by modulating the c-secretase pathway of the APP processing  , we wanted to see whether this was also the case in our in vivo experimental setting."
